snippet.textDisplay: When words are pure and the tune is traditional; it gives rise to melody. When melody is rendered by pure talent with unbridled energy coupled with years of relentless practice; comes melifluous music. The words could be understood and the soul is stirred. The melody could be felt as you are left with goose-bumps. The joy would infectiously transfer from head to mind to soul to face. You find out that you are in love with the world, oblivious to mayhem around. Brilliant is cliche. It's Unique !!

snippet.textDisplay: This is absolutely awesome! The song is a beautiful piece of folk inspired music, composed by the very talented Shantanu Moitra and the immaculate and flawless rendition of it, shows off the versatility of Kaushiki, the finest classical vocalist of her generation in India today. The use and treatment of the Bangla Khol (instead of tabla) is very cleverly done to give a unique texture to the rhythm.
snippet.textOriginal: This is absolutely awesome! The song is a beautiful piece of folk inspired music, composed by the very talented Shantanu Moitra and the immaculate and flawless rendition of it, shows off the versatility of Kaushiki, the finest classical vocalist of her generation in India today. The use and treatment of the Bangla Khol (instead of tabla) is very cleverly done to give a unique texture to the rhythm.
